WEBVTT

00:00:13.939 --> 00:00:14.439
Mr. Chen.

00:00:14.439 --> 00:00:15.264
Mr. Chen, let me.

00:00:15.660 --> 00:00:18.280
You two came
without giving me a heads-up.

00:00:19.000 --> 00:00:20.260
Look at the time.

00:00:21.460 --> 00:00:24.000
After work, we just want
some of your noodles to unwind.

00:00:26.739 --> 00:00:28.120
It's been a while since you came.

00:00:29.019 --> 00:00:30.660
Yes, it's all my fault.

00:00:30.660 --> 00:00:33.320
I admit it.
The company's been too busy lately.

00:00:33.320 --> 00:00:36.380
Guangcai often mentions you too,
but he's been swamped recently.

00:00:36.560 --> 00:00:38.000
He said he'd see you soon.

00:00:40.100 --> 00:00:41.020
You two chat first.

00:00:41.460 --> 00:00:42.000
Okay.

00:00:42.340 --> 00:00:43.700
Lights off when you leave.

00:00:43.700 --> 00:00:44.700
Get some rest early.

00:00:54.500 --> 00:00:57.340
Zhu Helai brought the police to me.

00:00:57.700 --> 00:00:58.520
I saw them.

00:01:02.020 --> 00:01:03.200
It's still about Xiaoliang.

00:01:03.560 --> 00:01:04.780
This day has finally come.

00:01:10.500 --> 00:01:11.500
No matter what happens,

00:01:13.000 --> 00:01:14.379
I'll be right there shielding you.

00:01:20.832 --> 00:01:23.424
(Outskirts of Shaguai Village,
Magou Town, Beiyan County)

00:01:31.560 --> 00:01:32.299
Help!

00:01:32.560 --> 00:01:33.920
Move!

00:01:33.920 --> 00:01:36.060
Someone, help!

00:01:37.340 --> 00:01:38.340
- Help!
- Move!

00:01:38.340 --> 00:01:39.420
Move!

00:01:40.200 --> 00:01:40.780
Move!

00:01:42.840 --> 00:01:43.640
Lijun!

00:01:44.680 --> 00:01:46.120
Lijun, open the door!

00:01:47.040 --> 00:01:47.840
Lijun!

00:01:48.280 --> 00:01:48.840
Coming.

00:01:49.700 --> 00:01:50.260
Qin.

00:01:55.680 --> 00:01:56.680
What's wrong?

00:01:57.260 --> 00:01:58.500
Take me away with you.

00:01:59.540 --> 00:02:00.620
The farther, the better.

00:02:05.400 --> 00:02:07.340
Qin, what's going on?

00:02:08.259 --> 00:02:10.360
It's snowing so heavily.
We're completely unprepared.

00:02:10.439 --> 00:02:11.439
Where could we even go?

00:02:12.840 --> 00:02:14.340
Did you have a fight with Guangcai?

00:02:14.400 --> 00:02:15.939
If he bullied you, I'll chew him out.

00:02:18.639 --> 00:02:19.400
Qin.

00:02:26.860 --> 00:02:28.360
You and Guangcai are engaged.

00:02:29.520 --> 00:02:30.580
I'm his brother.

00:02:31.520 --> 00:02:33.400
If we just leave without explanation,

00:02:33.740 --> 00:02:35.800
how will Guangcai live
with himself in the village?

00:02:37.139 --> 00:02:38.860
What happened? Tell me.

00:03:10.080 --> 00:03:11.020
Eat first.

00:03:18.912 --> 00:03:25.024
(Rongfa Noodle Shop)

00:04:46.112 --> 00:04:48.832
=The Silent Rift=

00:04:49.088 --> 00:04:51.816
=Episode 7=
(Scapegoats)

00:04:51.872 --> 00:04:53.824
(Meng Xiaoliang and Meng Guangcai
are not biologically father and son.)

00:04:56.800 --> 00:04:58.920
You two really know
how to keep your cool.

00:04:59.060 --> 00:05:00.360
Reporting to me only now?

00:05:01.420 --> 00:05:04.819
Chief, here's the thing.
Regarding this test result,

00:05:04.819 --> 00:05:07.500
we had the Provincial Department
colleagues double-check it

00:05:07.500 --> 00:05:09.540
and confirmed it
before reporting to you.

00:05:09.540 --> 00:05:10.800
Is this a report for me?

00:05:13.920 --> 00:05:15.560
Team Leader Zhang and Captain Li,

00:05:15.560 --> 00:05:18.240
you're both old cops.
I don't have to push you, right?

00:05:18.560 --> 00:05:19.420
Zhu Helai's

00:05:20.480 --> 00:05:22.048
supposedly solid evidence was flawed.

00:05:22.740 --> 00:05:24.980
Plus, his health
hasn't been great lately.

00:05:25.300 --> 00:05:28.100
Can we request to transfer him
back to Logistics?

00:05:28.100 --> 00:05:31.120
My master was instrumental
in catching Wang Dazhu.

00:05:31.120 --> 00:05:33.300
That was him breaking procedure
and getting lucky.

00:05:33.439 --> 00:05:35.180
Zhang Wei, could you stop defending him?

00:05:35.180 --> 00:05:37.800
After all these years,
what solid evidence does he have?

00:05:37.939 --> 00:05:39.680
His stubborn fixation on Meng Guangcai

00:05:39.680 --> 00:05:42.680
will derail
the entire task force's investigation,

00:05:42.680 --> 00:05:43.300
Chief.

00:05:46.300 --> 00:05:47.620
With years of persistence,

00:05:49.360 --> 00:05:50.680
intuition matters too.

00:05:52.100 --> 00:05:53.060
So you mean...

00:05:53.560 --> 00:05:55.060
What Chief Liu means is,

00:05:55.240 --> 00:05:59.480
as the leader, you should assign tasks
based on each officer's strengths.

00:06:01.680 --> 00:06:02.740
Is that what I meant?

00:06:03.300 --> 00:06:06.420
Chief, we'll get a breakthrough
with Wang Dazhu soon

00:06:06.860 --> 00:06:08.680
and identify the suspect list ASAP.

00:06:24.800 --> 00:06:27.744
(Meng Xiaoliang and Meng Guangcai
are not biologically father and son.)

00:06:37.680 --> 00:06:38.620
What are we eating?

00:06:39.860 --> 00:06:40.920
Shredded potatoes again?

00:06:42.480 --> 00:06:43.920
I've noticed,

00:06:44.560 --> 00:06:47.420
whenever Officer Zhu is deep in thought,
he shreds potatoes.

00:06:47.680 --> 00:06:50.300
Can you take it out
on some beef next time?

00:06:50.680 --> 00:06:52.120
Eating still doesn't shut you up.

00:06:54.560 --> 00:06:55.800
It's that test report.

00:06:56.300 --> 00:06:59.560
Chief Liu laid into Captain Zhang
last night. The whole floor heard it.

00:07:03.860 --> 00:07:06.240
We're in a tough spot right now.

00:07:06.860 --> 00:07:08.480
I reported to the chief yesterday.

00:07:08.860 --> 00:07:10.180
Chief Liu pointed out two things.

00:07:10.180 --> 00:07:13.540
First, speed up the interrogation
of Wang Dazhu.

00:07:14.040 --> 00:07:16.500
Second, start by tracking down Zuo Long
and Ma Zhongwu

00:07:16.860 --> 00:07:18.360
to identify the suspect list ASAP.

00:07:18.800 --> 00:07:21.040
Guys! Guys! Major discovery!

00:07:21.120 --> 00:07:22.980
Captain Li, where were you all morning?

00:07:23.600 --> 00:07:25.240
Captain Zhang, listen. Major discovery.

00:07:25.860 --> 00:07:28.939
After 1993,
Ma Zhongwu disappeared, right?

00:07:29.000 --> 00:07:31.240
We looked everywhere
but couldn't find any trace of him.

00:07:31.240 --> 00:07:34.100
So I thought, what?
Did he vanish into thin air?

00:07:34.620 --> 00:07:38.680
Turns out he was serving time elsewhere
and got the death penalty.

00:07:38.939 --> 00:07:40.384
During his death penalty review,

00:07:40.384 --> 00:07:42.860
(Criminal Entry Form)
he changed his name to Ma Dajun.

00:07:44.224 --> 00:07:49.242
(Babei City Detention Center)

00:07:57.480 --> 00:07:58.240
Ma Zhongwu.

00:07:58.480 --> 00:07:59.000
Here.

00:08:02.300 --> 00:08:05.360
If I confess,
can you reduce my sentence?

00:08:05.560 --> 00:08:07.740
Just got in, huh?
Don't know the rules yet?

00:08:08.740 --> 00:08:11.300
At this point, you think
you can negotiate terms with me?

00:08:12.860 --> 00:08:14.040
You're from Beiyan, right?

00:08:18.480 --> 00:08:19.360
What 'yan'?

00:08:19.360 --> 00:08:20.180
Beiyan.

00:08:21.300 --> 00:08:22.500
You're from Beiyan?

00:08:22.680 --> 00:08:23.600
Never heard of it.

00:08:24.360 --> 00:08:25.120
Ma Dajun,

00:08:26.439 --> 00:08:27.800
formerly known as Ma Zhongwu,

00:08:28.180 --> 00:08:29.184
was born in 1964.

00:08:29.280 --> 00:08:31.240
Once an employee
at Beiyan Machinery Factory,

00:08:31.680 --> 00:08:33.740
but fired for instigating a group brawl.

00:08:33.740 --> 00:08:37.740
We've verified your prior records
with local authorities.

00:08:37.740 --> 00:08:41.299
Alright, sir.
If you already know, why ask me?

00:08:41.679 --> 00:08:44.279
Besides, it's been ages
since I went back to Beiyan.

00:08:44.500 --> 00:08:48.740
You should remember what you've done,
no matter how long ago.

00:08:51.399 --> 00:08:52.672
Let me remind you.

00:08:52.929 --> 00:08:54.460
In June 1993,

00:08:54.899 --> 00:08:57.240
where were you and what were you doing?

00:09:00.399 --> 00:09:03.480
Let me think. 1993, right?

00:09:03.700 --> 00:09:05.019
Yes, 1993.

00:09:11.360 --> 00:09:12.320
I forgot.

00:09:13.460 --> 00:09:17.600
Ma Zhongwu trafficked drugs
around the southwest border around 1995.

00:09:17.980 --> 00:09:21.080
After fleeing back,
he assumed a whole new identity.

00:09:21.360 --> 00:09:23.519
Hence, no one knew him
as Ma Zhongwu afterward.

00:09:23.519 --> 00:09:25.440
From the records they sent over,

00:09:26.360 --> 00:09:29.620
Ma Zhongwu
didn't deny committing robbery.

00:09:29.620 --> 00:09:32.000
He's currently
in the death penalty review stage.

00:09:32.159 --> 00:09:33.860
Without this case,
he's a dead man walking.

00:09:34.120 --> 00:09:37.700
Judging by a death row inmate's mindset,

00:09:37.820 --> 00:09:40.580
Ma Zhongwu's silence
is a bid to cheat death.

00:09:41.159 --> 00:09:43.000
As long as he stays silent,
we keep looking.

00:09:43.000 --> 00:09:45.159
He can stall as long
as the case remains unsolved.

00:09:45.620 --> 00:09:49.240
I say we leverage this to pressure
Meng Guangcai and Wang Dazhu.

00:09:49.659 --> 00:09:51.019
Meanwhile, we pursue Zuo Long.

00:09:53.360 --> 00:09:55.120
What's wrong, Master? Any objections?

00:09:55.500 --> 00:09:58.000
No objections. None at all.

00:10:00.740 --> 00:10:02.120
Go on, continue.

00:10:02.860 --> 00:10:05.080
Given Xue Qin's current story,

00:10:05.360 --> 00:10:07.860
Zuo Long is likely
Meng Xiaoliang's father.

00:10:07.860 --> 00:10:10.290
I plan to focus next on

00:10:10.290 --> 00:10:12.320
tracing Zuo Long's extended connections.

00:10:12.320 --> 00:10:15.240
See if we can uncover new leads.

00:10:16.159 --> 00:10:20.080
Master, this is a task force meeting.

00:10:20.080 --> 00:10:22.120
If you have any objections, speak up.
Let's discuss.

00:10:22.120 --> 00:10:24.580
We're being led by the nose.

00:10:25.700 --> 00:10:27.980
Zuo Long and Ma Zhongwu
are both smoke screens.

00:10:28.120 --> 00:10:30.519
Meng Guangcai and the other two
are like real brothers.

00:10:30.519 --> 00:10:33.700
If we ignore Jiao Lijun,
we're just doing this the hard way.

00:10:33.700 --> 00:10:34.840
Fine, Officer Zhu.

00:10:35.232 --> 00:10:37.120
You've worked this case for 20 years.

00:10:37.120 --> 00:10:39.159
Tell us, what should we do?

00:10:39.159 --> 00:10:40.980
Give me the order,
and I'll execute. Alright?

00:10:41.620 --> 00:10:43.659
Hold on, Captain Li.

00:10:44.700 --> 00:10:47.120
It's fine. Continue, go on.

00:10:47.120 --> 00:10:49.620
Extended connections, right?
Extended connections.

00:10:49.940 --> 00:10:53.320
When Zuo Long vanished in the 1990s,
I traced his extended connections.

00:10:53.700 --> 00:10:55.639
Beyond local thugs from his hometown,

00:10:55.639 --> 00:10:57.779
only his wife
and brother-in-law remained.

00:10:58.000 --> 00:11:01.039
Captain Li, I can give you
the extended connections list.

00:11:13.856 --> 00:11:15.519
(4th Interrogation)

00:11:15.519 --> 00:11:19.240
Mr. Meng, you seem well,
adapting quickly to the new environment.

00:11:21.320 --> 00:11:25.039
With the officers taking care of me,
life's been good.

00:11:26.700 --> 00:11:28.740
What questions today? Be direct.

00:11:28.740 --> 00:11:32.019
You once said
you'd heard of the 6.10 robbery,

00:11:32.399 --> 00:11:35.000
and the robbers were Zuo Long
and Ma Zhongwu, correct?

00:11:37.039 --> 00:11:38.240
I did say that.

00:11:38.240 --> 00:11:41.539
Then recall the circumstances
under which you heard it.

00:11:41.899 --> 00:11:42.700
And who told you?

00:11:44.240 --> 00:11:46.159
That was nearly 20 years ago.

00:11:48.279 --> 00:11:50.000
Many were talking about it back then.

00:11:50.539 --> 00:11:52.539
But I can't recall who told me.

00:11:54.120 --> 00:11:55.260
My answer's fine, right?

00:11:55.260 --> 00:11:56.240
Sure.

00:11:56.399 --> 00:11:59.200
You claim
you never participated in the robbery.

00:12:00.360 --> 00:12:01.120
Correct.

00:12:01.620 --> 00:12:05.360
Meaning if we find Zuo Long
and Ma Zhongwu,

00:12:06.080 --> 00:12:08.240
your suspicion
will be completely cleared.

00:12:10.039 --> 00:12:11.000
So?

00:12:13.159 --> 00:12:14.519
We've found one of them,

00:12:16.159 --> 00:12:17.240
Ma Zhongwu.

00:12:27.159 --> 00:12:29.740
You said Ma Zhongwu and Zuo Long
made you rob the credit union.

00:12:29.740 --> 00:12:30.820
How did you three meet?

00:12:34.620 --> 00:12:36.620
Cut it. Listen to me.

00:12:36.940 --> 00:12:39.519
We've got Ma Zhongwu.
Better start cooperating.

00:12:39.860 --> 00:12:42.860
I have stomach pain!
Get me a doctor! Doctor!

00:12:48.992 --> 00:12:52.360
(Crack down on crime.
Protect the people.)

00:12:52.360 --> 00:12:53.360
Captain Li. Captain Li.

00:12:58.279 --> 00:12:59.539
How's Wang Dazhu doing?

00:13:01.120 --> 00:13:03.440
Being difficult. Won't say a word.

00:13:03.620 --> 00:13:04.860
Just wasting time there.

00:13:07.000 --> 00:13:08.940
Meng Guangcai's unusually calm, though.

00:13:09.440 --> 00:13:10.539
No reaction either.

00:13:11.820 --> 00:13:14.320
Captain Zhang, can I ask a favor?

00:13:14.580 --> 00:13:16.360
Can you send your master back to rest?

00:13:19.620 --> 00:13:21.399
It's Chief Liu's intention.

00:13:22.500 --> 00:13:25.740
Chief Liu has his plans. Focus on unity.

00:13:27.120 --> 00:13:29.240
I hate when you play the appeaser.

00:13:29.539 --> 00:13:31.740
Whose apprentice are you?
Zhu Helai's, right?

00:13:32.000 --> 00:13:33.952
Why start imitating
Chief Liu's 'unity' now?

00:13:34.159 --> 00:13:35.500
Unity brings progress.

00:13:43.360 --> 00:13:44.039
(Task Force Office)
Come on, Liang.

00:13:45.860 --> 00:13:47.159
Captain Li, we've got something.

00:13:47.820 --> 00:13:49.200
It's Zuo Long's extended network.

00:13:52.240 --> 00:13:53.000
Great hand today.

00:13:53.000 --> 00:13:53.620
Red Dragon.

00:13:53.620 --> 00:13:54.360
Play this one.

00:13:55.159 --> 00:13:55.940
What are you doing?

00:13:57.120 --> 00:13:57.860
I win.

00:13:59.000 --> 00:14:00.120
Who are you looking for?

00:14:02.740 --> 00:14:03.399
Nice hand.

00:14:04.000 --> 00:14:04.820
What's the stake?

00:14:05.200 --> 00:14:06.240
Who are you?

00:14:07.240 --> 00:14:08.659
Come have a chat with us.

00:14:08.659 --> 00:14:09.360
Busy.

00:14:10.039 --> 00:14:10.659
Let's go.

00:14:11.320 --> 00:14:12.320
Who are you?

00:14:15.440 --> 00:14:15.980
Easy.

00:14:17.240 --> 00:14:18.000
Easy, easy.

00:14:18.000 --> 00:14:20.659
What's going on?
Why did you bring me here?

00:14:22.159 --> 00:14:23.360
I was fine in Qingchuan City.

00:14:23.360 --> 00:14:25.500
Why did you drag me all the way here?

00:14:25.620 --> 00:14:28.519
Why didn't you say you're cops?
Manhandling me like that.

00:14:28.700 --> 00:14:31.360
Is this how you
treat a law-abiding citizen?

00:14:31.620 --> 00:14:34.740
You need to explain
what's going on here.

00:14:35.000 --> 00:14:37.240
If you don't, I won't let this go.

00:14:37.240 --> 00:14:38.039
Stop shouting.

00:14:39.200 --> 00:14:40.120
Look at where you are.

00:14:40.899 --> 00:14:42.480
This is no place for a tantrum.

00:14:43.080 --> 00:14:45.279
What place?
It's just the police station.

00:14:45.860 --> 00:14:49.039
I was in and out of the police station
while you were still in diapers.

00:14:49.320 --> 00:14:52.940
Besides, the case our family reported
back then still hasn't been solved.

00:14:53.039 --> 00:14:55.519
Don't give me that attitude, rookie.

00:14:55.860 --> 00:14:58.860
Perfect. We brought you in today
precisely for that matter.

00:15:03.120 --> 00:15:03.779
Here.

00:15:04.740 --> 00:15:07.360
Take a look. This is your
communication record online.

00:15:07.360 --> 00:15:08.279
Tell us.

00:15:08.659 --> 00:15:11.320
(Shi Sinian)
Who is this 'good friend' of yours?

00:15:14.120 --> 00:15:15.779
Not familiar. Don't know him.

00:15:17.659 --> 00:15:19.700
Probably just a netizen.

00:15:19.700 --> 00:15:20.620
Netizen?

00:15:21.659 --> 00:15:22.700
All these years,

00:15:23.320 --> 00:15:26.000
this 'netizen' has transferred money
to you seven times.

00:15:26.159 --> 00:15:26.779
'Not familiar'?

00:15:34.700 --> 00:15:37.120
Zuo Long disappeared in 1991.

00:15:37.440 --> 00:15:40.120
His wife and her brother
reported the case that same year.

00:15:40.120 --> 00:15:42.290
Officer Zhu at Magou Town Police Station

00:15:42.290 --> 00:15:44.240
was the first to handle this case.

00:15:44.240 --> 00:15:45.024
Alright,

00:15:45.472 --> 00:15:48.759
based on the latest information
we have now,

00:15:50.820 --> 00:15:54.460
in early 2006,
the brother of Zuo Long's wife

00:15:55.580 --> 00:15:58.940
first made contact online with someone
using an anonymous identity.

00:15:58.940 --> 00:16:01.740
Up to now, the two
have been in contact 15 times.

00:16:01.740 --> 00:16:04.259
They've made seven online transactions.

00:16:05.899 --> 00:16:08.139
During this period,
guided by that anonymous person,

00:16:08.539 --> 00:16:12.740
he changed his email password
and transfer methods multiple times.

00:16:12.740 --> 00:16:15.580
Both sides were very cautious,
neither revealing their true identities.

00:16:15.820 --> 00:16:19.159
But from the online chat records
we've gathered,

00:16:19.159 --> 00:16:20.120
we can basically confirm

00:16:20.360 --> 00:16:24.539
that the anonymous person is Zuo Long,
the key suspect we're looking for.

00:16:24.539 --> 00:16:28.399
Can we use this information source
to track Zuo Long's current location?

00:16:28.500 --> 00:16:30.620
By tracing their transfer information,

00:16:30.620 --> 00:16:34.440
we can basically confirm Zuo Long's
activity range is within Southeast Asia.

00:16:34.440 --> 00:16:36.659
But he keeps moving around.

00:16:36.860 --> 00:16:39.820
If the guy's abroad,
this operation could drag on.

00:16:40.120 --> 00:16:42.320
Someone wants us
to drag this operation on.

00:16:47.820 --> 00:16:48.620
Evidence.

00:16:50.240 --> 00:16:52.779
We need evidence to work a case, right?

00:17:12.896 --> 00:17:14.592
(Wang Lanju, Ma Zhongwu's Mother)

00:17:17.559 --> 00:17:20.559
My son was very mischievous
when he was little.

00:17:22.240 --> 00:17:25.039
But he was very filial towards me.

00:17:27.599 --> 00:17:30.000
Early in the nineties, he went out.

00:17:32.099 --> 00:17:35.200
At first, he said
he was going out to do business,

00:17:36.099 --> 00:17:39.740
and he'd send me money
once he made his fortune.

00:17:39.799 --> 00:17:43.980
It's good when kids grow up
and make something of themselves.

00:17:44.180 --> 00:17:48.799
I couldn't always complain
about him never being home.

00:17:49.019 --> 00:17:50.299
But who knew...

00:17:51.799 --> 00:17:52.799
Later on...

00:17:53.680 --> 00:17:55.940
Later on, there was no news.

00:17:57.599 --> 00:17:58.740
All these years,

00:18:00.339 --> 00:18:02.980
not a single bit of news.

00:18:04.299 --> 00:18:05.319
Do you remember

00:18:06.819 --> 00:18:08.579
what year he left home?

00:18:10.279 --> 00:18:11.380
He left

00:18:12.940 --> 00:18:16.279
in 1993 or 1994?

00:18:17.299 --> 00:18:20.019
I can't remember clearly.
Getting old and muddled.

00:18:21.039 --> 00:18:22.920
Did he ever send money home after that?

00:18:23.980 --> 00:18:25.980
He used to send money in the nineties,

00:18:26.960 --> 00:18:28.799
but then nothing.

00:18:29.200 --> 00:18:30.720
When he sent money,

00:18:31.680 --> 00:18:32.980
which account did he send it to?

00:18:34.819 --> 00:18:36.019
Account?

00:18:52.539 --> 00:18:56.240
Officer, you've been here twice now.

00:18:58.420 --> 00:19:03.200
Has my son gotten
into some kind of trouble?

00:19:06.039 --> 00:19:08.720
Officer, please.

00:19:09.440 --> 00:19:14.039
If you know anything, just tell me.
Tell me.

00:19:14.960 --> 00:19:20.019
What mother doesn't worry about her son?

00:19:22.559 --> 00:19:24.440
All these years...

00:19:25.700 --> 00:19:29.200
All these years
without a single message from him.

00:19:33.519 --> 00:19:34.880
Zhongwu.

00:19:40.559 --> 00:19:42.079
Not a word.

00:19:42.784 --> 00:19:44.740
(Crack down on crime.
Protect the people.)

00:19:44.740 --> 00:19:47.599
This passbook and this bank card

00:19:49.220 --> 00:19:50.720
were used by Ma Zhongwu's mother.

00:19:51.079 --> 00:19:54.599
I also pulled some bank deposit
and withdrawal records,

00:19:54.920 --> 00:19:56.320
plus other info from back then.

00:19:56.680 --> 00:19:57.980
In 1994,

00:19:58.519 --> 00:20:02.839
Ma Zhongwu's mother
received two remittances.

00:20:03.039 --> 00:20:04.224
(Beiyan Bank Detailed Transaction Record)
Then, for many years after that,

00:20:04.864 --> 00:20:06.220
she didn't receive any money.

00:20:06.220 --> 00:20:10.039
Until 2006, several more remittances
suddenly appeared in her account.

00:20:10.380 --> 00:20:12.220
Based on the case file
from the local police,

00:20:12.440 --> 00:20:16.180
Ma Zhongwu's criminal activities
were along the southwestern border.

00:20:16.460 --> 00:20:19.680
It matches the clues I found
about Zuo Long. What?

00:20:20.720 --> 00:20:24.099
Ma Zhongwu's mother's bank account
hadn't received any money for years.

00:20:24.099 --> 00:20:26.719
I asked her
when she switched to this card.

00:20:26.719 --> 00:20:28.220
She said it was 2006.

00:20:28.220 --> 00:20:31.240
The bank said her passbook was outdated
and she needed to switch to a card.

00:20:31.240 --> 00:20:33.460
She wasn't familiar,
so the bank staff did it for her.

00:20:33.460 --> 00:20:35.059
She hadn't withdrawn money for years

00:20:35.059 --> 00:20:37.240
and didn't know how to operate an ATM,

00:20:37.240 --> 00:20:39.220
so she didn't know
there was still money in it.

00:20:40.180 --> 00:20:44.880
At this point in time in 2006,
Ma Zhongwu and Zuo Long

00:20:45.579 --> 00:20:47.819
sending money home
as if they'd coordinated it.

00:20:47.819 --> 00:20:50.380
Right. That's what doesn't make sense.

00:20:50.779 --> 00:20:53.500
Zuo Long and Ma Zhongwu
seemed to have planned it.

00:20:53.500 --> 00:20:57.480
They both sent large sums home
around the same time that year.

00:20:58.380 --> 00:21:00.799
Is that possible?
Is that just a coincidence?

00:21:00.799 --> 00:21:03.200
Unless the money wasn't sent by them.

00:21:03.460 --> 00:21:06.980
If I were Meng Guangcai,
I'd definitely find two scapegoats.

00:21:07.140 --> 00:21:09.079
The kind who are dead and can't testify.

00:21:09.779 --> 00:21:13.079
Zuo Long and Ma Zhongwu both had
criminal records, and both disappeared.

00:21:13.240 --> 00:21:14.700
They were the perfect targets.

00:21:15.200 --> 00:21:18.440
But he didn't expect
that Ma Zhongwu didn't disappear.

00:21:18.819 --> 00:21:20.680
He changed his name
and was sentenced to death.

00:21:20.680 --> 00:21:22.720
Us finding this Ma Zhongwu

00:21:22.720 --> 00:21:24.960
must have been a mistake
for Meng Guangcai.

00:21:25.920 --> 00:21:26.799
Of course, Captain Li,

00:21:27.519 --> 00:21:28.819
I'm just speculating.

00:21:29.680 --> 00:21:30.740
I don't have any evidence.

00:21:31.299 --> 00:21:33.680
So I think that in 2006,

00:21:34.720 --> 00:21:37.220
someone deliberately used remittances

00:21:37.799 --> 00:21:40.720
to create the illusion that those two
were still at large abroad.

00:21:43.000 --> 00:21:43.980
So basically,

00:21:45.000 --> 00:21:46.539
Meng Guangcai and his gang

00:21:47.000 --> 00:21:49.799
started setting things up abroad
as early as five years ago,

00:21:51.099 --> 00:21:54.480
just waiting for us
to dig up the clues they buried?

00:21:54.700 --> 00:21:57.579
According to you,
these guys are practically psychic.

00:21:57.740 --> 00:21:59.380
You don't know Meng Guangcai
well enough.

00:22:00.200 --> 00:22:02.019
To protect the wealth he has today,

00:22:02.019 --> 00:22:04.740
creating some traces
is no big deal for him.

00:22:05.680 --> 00:22:09.220
2006 was absolutely crucial
for Meng Guangcai.

00:22:11.539 --> 00:22:15.059
I'm just offering some thoughts,
no concrete solutions.

00:22:16.599 --> 00:22:20.039
I'm not feeling well today.
I'll head back first.

00:22:24.380 --> 00:22:26.220
Dad, you're back.

00:22:26.500 --> 00:22:27.319
I'm back.

00:22:33.240 --> 00:22:33.819
Qianqian,

00:22:35.019 --> 00:22:35.819
where's your mom?

00:22:36.140 --> 00:22:37.980
Mom's on the night shift
at the supermarket.

00:22:37.980 --> 00:22:39.279
I'll cook for you two.

00:22:40.079 --> 00:22:41.720
You go study. I'll cook.

00:22:42.599 --> 00:22:43.220
Freeze.

00:22:43.680 --> 00:22:45.819
I suggest you immediately
drop your weapon,

00:22:45.819 --> 00:22:48.680
stop resisting, and go sit outside
to wait for dinner.

00:22:49.720 --> 00:22:50.420
Okay.

00:22:51.099 --> 00:22:54.299
I suggest you focus
on the primary objective.

00:22:54.680 --> 00:22:56.672
Focus on your college prep.
Don't get distracted.

00:22:57.460 --> 00:22:59.424
Sir, the mission will be accomplished.

00:23:02.368 --> 00:23:05.299
Alright. Call me when you're done.

00:23:53.440 --> 00:23:57.508
(Me: Don't rush. Tell me more
about what happened in Guangnan.)

00:23:58.400 --> 00:24:01.190
(I was invited to Principal Chen's
new noodle restaurant.)

00:24:01.190 --> 00:24:03.552
(The bold sign above the entrance
read Rongfa Noodle Shop.)

00:24:07.072 --> 00:24:11.148
(Rongfa Noodle Shop, Beiyan County)

00:24:17.200 --> 00:24:18.539
Grand opening!

00:24:18.740 --> 00:24:20.279
- Grand opening!
- Grand opening!

00:24:20.279 --> 00:24:21.380
Thanks! Thanks!

00:24:21.579 --> 00:24:22.779
Thank you! Thank you!

00:24:22.779 --> 00:24:24.799
Here, Third Uncle, take one.

00:24:24.799 --> 00:24:25.460
Coming!

00:24:25.920 --> 00:24:27.200
Nice renovation, Principal Chen.

00:24:27.519 --> 00:24:29.059
I knew you'd come.

00:24:29.059 --> 00:24:29.579
Here.

00:24:30.019 --> 00:24:31.740
Gentlemen, please take a look.

00:24:31.740 --> 00:24:32.460
Business cards?

00:24:32.460 --> 00:24:35.000
Yes, business cards.
Wang Dazhu, Shaguai Building Materials.

00:24:35.319 --> 00:24:36.220
The boss?

00:24:36.259 --> 00:24:37.579
Sales Manager.

00:24:37.579 --> 00:24:39.099
Very impressive.

00:24:39.099 --> 00:24:42.460
Guangcai is the president, a big boss.

00:24:42.460 --> 00:24:44.460
And Lijun is the vice president.

00:24:44.460 --> 00:24:46.460
Now Dazhu has made it too, see?

00:24:46.460 --> 00:24:48.180
Wait, hold on, Mr. Chen.

00:24:48.740 --> 00:24:49.819
General Manager Wang.

00:24:51.019 --> 00:24:51.960
And yours.

00:24:51.960 --> 00:24:53.180
Who? Mine?

00:24:53.180 --> 00:24:53.728
Yes.

00:24:53.824 --> 00:24:57.220
Chairman Chen Rongfa
of Rongfa Noodle Shop.

00:24:57.720 --> 00:25:00.460
From now on, just like me, hand one out
whenever you meet someone.

00:25:00.460 --> 00:25:03.680
Don't waste your money on this.

00:25:03.680 --> 00:25:04.180
Thank you.

00:25:04.420 --> 00:25:04.980
Thanks.

00:25:05.500 --> 00:25:08.200
Guangcai is quite promising.

00:25:08.839 --> 00:25:10.039
It's Dazhu's gesture.

00:25:10.640 --> 00:25:11.700
It's so grand.

00:25:12.640 --> 00:25:13.680
Officer Zhu,

00:25:14.140 --> 00:25:17.579
you're practically
half a villager of Shaguai.

00:25:17.720 --> 00:25:20.240
I'm especially glad
you could come today.

00:25:20.240 --> 00:25:22.799
Please try our Shaguai noodles.

00:25:23.240 --> 00:25:26.460
No need to say 'please.'
I've been wanting to try your cooking.

00:25:26.579 --> 00:25:30.819
And Guangcai mentioned he's been
craving your noodles since he was a kid.

00:25:32.960 --> 00:25:35.920
Guangcai had a tough life early on.

00:25:35.920 --> 00:25:39.599
His parents passed away young
during a terrible blizzard.

00:25:39.819 --> 00:25:43.339
Back then,
I searched all over the Gobi Desert.

00:25:43.880 --> 00:25:45.720
He was the only one I found.

00:25:45.720 --> 00:25:46.220
Good.

00:25:46.420 --> 00:25:47.880
- No clue how to raise a kid.
- Not bad today.

00:25:48.220 --> 00:25:49.680
I just made noodles for him.

00:25:50.279 --> 00:25:52.460
He never forgot that taste.

00:25:52.460 --> 00:25:56.240
Mr. Meng, I'm Wang Dazhu, sales manager
of Shaguai Building Materials.

00:25:56.240 --> 00:25:57.079
Get out of here.

00:25:57.960 --> 00:26:01.960
When times were hard,
he helped me open this noodle shop.

00:26:02.680 --> 00:26:04.579
Here, son, have another piece of meat.

00:26:06.039 --> 00:26:07.079
You're still hungry, huh?

00:26:07.299 --> 00:26:08.940
Your business must be booming.

00:26:08.940 --> 00:26:11.460
I'm just worried you won't be able
to handle the crowds.

00:26:11.539 --> 00:26:12.880
It is overwhelming.

00:26:13.220 --> 00:26:16.460
Guangcai. Guangcai. Come here.

00:26:16.460 --> 00:26:18.579
Go on, take the orange.
I'll take your bowl.

00:26:19.380 --> 00:26:21.200
Guangcai, come here.

00:26:21.200 --> 00:26:23.640
Keep Officer Zhu company for me.

00:26:23.640 --> 00:26:25.599
I need to handle something in the back.

00:26:25.980 --> 00:26:26.779
- Go ahead.
- Come on.

00:26:27.019 --> 00:26:27.819
Sit.

00:26:27.819 --> 00:26:28.700
Mr. Chen, well.

00:26:29.779 --> 00:26:30.819
He says he wants more.

00:26:31.279 --> 00:26:32.220
Go with Grandpa.

00:26:32.640 --> 00:26:34.880
Just a little.
He's already had plenty today.

00:26:39.500 --> 00:26:40.200
- Here, pickles.
- Have some too.

00:26:40.200 --> 00:26:42.299
No. You go ahead. Here, some pickles.

00:26:42.299 --> 00:26:43.059
Empty bowl.

00:26:57.640 --> 00:26:58.779
Tastes good, right?

00:26:59.819 --> 00:27:01.019
The noodles really are good.

00:27:07.539 --> 00:27:08.700
You've been busy lately.

00:27:09.240 --> 00:27:10.720
Haven't seen you at my place in ages.

00:27:10.720 --> 00:27:11.680
Just running around.

00:27:12.279 --> 00:27:13.536
Just got back from out of town.

00:27:14.599 --> 00:27:15.440
Where'd you go?

00:27:17.220 --> 00:27:17.819
Jinwan City.

00:27:18.700 --> 00:27:19.819
Still working the 6.10 case.

00:27:20.339 --> 00:27:22.559
Weren't you in Jinwan at the time too?

00:27:25.920 --> 00:27:26.480
Yeah.

00:27:28.140 --> 00:27:29.319
I was in Jinwan at the time.

00:27:29.740 --> 00:27:31.740
But that place and I never got along.

00:27:32.559 --> 00:27:33.480
Didn't land any work.

00:27:34.319 --> 00:27:35.460
Even got into a fight.

00:27:35.720 --> 00:27:37.920
The boss from back then remembered you.

00:27:38.240 --> 00:27:41.519
He said he remembered you from Shaguai
and you could really fight.

00:27:43.779 --> 00:27:44.700
'Could fight'?

00:27:46.339 --> 00:27:47.839
Local ties beat foreign might.

00:27:47.839 --> 00:27:49.059
It's much easier now.

00:27:50.599 --> 00:27:53.240
There's a highway.
No more taking just the train.

00:27:55.380 --> 00:27:57.339
Any progress with the investigation?

00:27:57.720 --> 00:27:59.180
Too much time has passed.

00:27:59.960 --> 00:28:01.059
No new leads.

00:28:01.460 --> 00:28:03.240
You were in Jinwan then too.

00:28:03.319 --> 00:28:05.839
If you've got time, I'd like to talk.

00:28:06.240 --> 00:28:07.240
Okay.

00:28:17.339 --> 00:28:17.960
Hello?

00:28:18.720 --> 00:28:19.440
Mr. Hao.

00:28:21.740 --> 00:28:22.779
I'll head back right away.

00:28:23.140 --> 00:28:25.319
Got it. Don't worry. Alright.

00:28:27.339 --> 00:28:28.200
Well,

00:28:30.240 --> 00:28:30.740
Zhu,

00:28:31.839 --> 00:28:33.920
there's something at the market.
I need to go back.

00:28:34.140 --> 00:28:36.640
How about we meet up tonight?

00:28:36.799 --> 00:28:38.079
Drinks on me, and we can talk.

00:28:38.319 --> 00:28:39.039
Guangcai.

00:28:40.240 --> 00:28:43.039
Let me remind you.
Stay away from the Hao brothers.

00:28:45.640 --> 00:28:46.500
Right.

00:28:47.319 --> 00:28:50.240
Lijun, let's head back to the market.

00:28:51.019 --> 00:28:53.319
Xue Qin, I'm going back
to the market now.

00:28:54.019 --> 00:28:55.640
Mr. Chen, we'll come back later.

00:28:55.640 --> 00:28:56.319
Okay.

00:28:59.200 --> 00:29:00.099
Take your time, Zhu.

00:29:08.416 --> 00:29:09.740
(Tile Processing Plant,
Wanchuang Stone Wholesale)

00:29:09.740 --> 00:29:11.000
No electric stove, okay?

00:29:11.220 --> 00:29:13.980
These boxes
can't be left in the hallway.

00:29:13.980 --> 00:29:15.240
We'll move them later.

00:29:15.240 --> 00:29:16.352
Look at these wires.

00:29:17.056 --> 00:29:18.599
The aging is severe.

00:29:19.799 --> 00:29:22.839
This part here needs immediate repair.

00:29:23.220 --> 00:29:25.420
This is serious. All potential hazards.

00:29:25.420 --> 00:29:26.220
Okay, okay.

00:29:27.240 --> 00:29:29.920
Your fire safety officer here
is practically useless.

00:29:30.420 --> 00:29:32.680
If there's a fire,

00:29:33.240 --> 00:29:34.539
it's a huge problem.

00:29:34.839 --> 00:29:37.160
I'll clear out this hallway later.

00:29:38.599 --> 00:29:41.559
As for these shops
storing flammable materials,

00:29:41.819 --> 00:29:43.960
if they don't fix it
by the deadline, expect fines.

00:29:44.460 --> 00:29:45.819
We'll fix it seriously.

00:29:46.700 --> 00:29:48.240
Isn't it just about fire safety?

00:29:48.519 --> 00:29:50.299
I heard. No big deal.

00:29:50.299 --> 00:29:53.059
Just give them some cash later.
Guaranteed no trouble.

00:29:54.519 --> 00:29:56.460
Got it, Hongliang. I'll handle it.

00:29:57.440 --> 00:29:59.799
Just go ahead and do it boldly.

00:30:00.319 --> 00:30:02.079
Besides, didn't my brother say it?

00:30:02.440 --> 00:30:06.170
From now on, you represent us brothers
at Baima Market.

00:30:06.592 --> 00:30:07.240
Got it?

00:30:07.240 --> 00:30:07.740
Got it.

00:30:07.740 --> 00:30:09.090
Just go for it.

00:30:09.090 --> 00:30:10.220
The better you perform,

00:30:10.460 --> 00:30:13.200
the more time we'll have
to discuss bigger deals.

00:30:13.460 --> 00:30:14.500
Yeah, big deals.

00:30:16.059 --> 00:30:17.519
Is it a big deal today too?

00:30:21.400 --> 00:30:24.400
Don't worry about things
that don't concern you.

00:30:26.279 --> 00:30:27.339
It's for your own good.

00:30:28.000 --> 00:30:29.079
That smile suits you well.

00:30:29.079 --> 00:30:29.799
Head back now.

00:30:30.079 --> 00:30:31.059
Then I'll head back.

00:30:31.140 --> 00:30:32.279
You can rest easy.

00:30:39.240 --> 00:30:40.299
He's here.

00:30:41.980 --> 00:30:43.579
Is it done?

00:30:45.240 --> 00:30:46.920
Let's grab some late-night eats.

00:30:47.319 --> 00:30:50.380
Look how chubby you've gotten,
always eating late at night.

00:30:50.380 --> 00:30:51.500
You're going to bankrupt me.

00:30:51.500 --> 00:30:54.140
I'm starving.
I could eat a whole pig right now.

00:30:54.140 --> 00:30:57.019
Guangcai, those two scoundrels
haven't given you trouble, have they?

00:30:57.740 --> 00:30:58.380
No.

00:31:00.079 --> 00:31:01.000
Their joy won't last.

00:31:01.720 --> 00:31:03.740
I heard many merchants in the market

00:31:04.140 --> 00:31:07.180
are staging a strike
due to the management fee.

00:31:07.880 --> 00:31:10.599
Let's use this opportunity
to teach those two scoundrels a lesson.

00:31:10.920 --> 00:31:13.319
Let them strike. The bigger, the better.

00:31:14.279 --> 00:31:15.460
Let's go for late-night eats.

00:31:15.460 --> 00:31:17.079
I'll bankrupt you.

00:31:17.200 --> 00:31:19.640
What did that businessman
in Guangnan call you?

00:31:26.099 --> 00:31:28.319
What, really scared I'll bankrupt you?

00:31:29.799 --> 00:31:30.480
- Guangcai.
- Come on.

00:31:30.480 --> 00:31:31.339
Let's go.

00:31:33.240 --> 00:31:35.720
Officer Zhu, look.

00:31:36.079 --> 00:31:38.559
You've come to our Baima Market
so many times.

00:31:38.700 --> 00:31:40.480
We haven't had a chance
to get acquainted.

00:31:40.980 --> 00:31:43.680
Today, whatever you ask us brothers,

00:31:43.680 --> 00:31:45.579
we'll cooperate fully.

00:31:45.579 --> 00:31:47.420
Let's have a drink.
Not too much to ask, right?

00:31:47.480 --> 00:31:49.980
I'm allergic to alcohol.
Otherwise, I'd really drink.

00:31:51.319 --> 00:31:54.220
Officer Zhu, please don't be like that.

00:31:54.220 --> 00:31:56.099
We finally managed
to have a meal with you.

00:31:56.460 --> 00:31:59.099
We brothers genuinely want
to be friends with you.

00:31:59.099 --> 00:32:00.960
We picked the place
and arranged the dishes.

00:32:01.460 --> 00:32:02.599
We put in enough thought.

00:32:02.799 --> 00:32:06.019
Being like this
is a bit inconsiderate of you.

00:32:06.220 --> 00:32:07.460
Exactly, Officer Zhu.

00:32:07.799 --> 00:32:09.839
You finally invited us brothers out once

00:32:10.420 --> 00:32:13.960
and even specifically told us
to keep it from Guangcai, right?

00:32:14.319 --> 00:32:17.299
Alright, I'll be honest
with you brothers.

00:32:18.000 --> 00:32:21.019
I came today just to ask something.

00:32:21.180 --> 00:32:25.599
Back in 1995, When Meng Guangcai
rented your shop to run his business,

00:32:26.579 --> 00:32:29.779
what were his basic circumstances?

00:32:36.720 --> 00:32:37.240
Look,

00:32:38.779 --> 00:32:40.140
this meal

00:32:40.940 --> 00:32:42.079
gets interesting now.

00:32:48.416 --> 00:32:49.720
(Beiyan County Hospital)

00:32:49.720 --> 00:32:52.099
Laosan, Qianqian is really smart.

00:32:53.380 --> 00:32:54.259
That part

00:32:55.140 --> 00:32:56.339
definitely takes after you.

00:32:56.579 --> 00:32:59.380
And she's adjusted really well in class.

00:32:59.539 --> 00:33:01.880
Her grades are excellent.

00:33:02.599 --> 00:33:05.279
Each time she brings home
her test papers, she yells,

00:33:05.819 --> 00:33:07.579
"Dad, sign it! Dad, sign it!"

00:33:08.440 --> 00:33:12.640
So, I've been enjoying
that blessing for you.

00:33:14.240 --> 00:33:15.579
If you can hear me,

00:33:20.319 --> 00:33:21.920
just open your eyes sooner

00:33:23.220 --> 00:33:24.039
and respond.

00:33:24.220 --> 00:33:25.440
While Qianqian is still young,

00:33:27.059 --> 00:33:28.319
I'll give her back to you.

00:33:31.819 --> 00:33:32.940
With a couple more years,

00:33:33.740 --> 00:33:35.519
I might not be willing to give her back.

00:33:39.480 --> 00:33:42.059
The case is not solved yet.

00:33:42.059 --> 00:33:44.839
But I'm not slacking off.
I've been on it.

00:33:46.240 --> 00:33:47.299
All these years,

00:33:48.440 --> 00:33:50.839
I've checked almost everyone
who needed checking.

00:33:52.000 --> 00:33:56.779
And I've sifted through
all the potential leads again and again.

00:33:56.779 --> 00:33:58.700
Now, actually, vaguely,

00:33:59.819 --> 00:34:01.000
I have a suspect in mind.

00:34:02.740 --> 00:34:03.960
But Laosan,

00:34:05.740 --> 00:34:06.960
though I suspect him,

00:34:08.800 --> 00:34:10.000
on the day it happened,

00:34:11.139 --> 00:34:12.960
he was indeed in Jinwan City.

00:34:13.739 --> 00:34:14.920
Lots of people saw him.

00:34:16.559 --> 00:34:18.500
If you say his business is shady,

00:34:20.219 --> 00:34:21.500
but when you ask around,

00:34:22.960 --> 00:34:24.559
there really aren't any obvious flaws.

00:34:26.820 --> 00:34:28.960
You know how eager I am
to solve this case,

00:34:32.079 --> 00:34:33.000
but I also

00:34:34.960 --> 00:34:36.539
really don't want to believe it's him.

00:34:38.199 --> 00:34:39.760
Am I crazy?

00:34:40.960 --> 00:34:43.880
How about you get up?
Get up and help me analyze this.

00:34:45.880 --> 00:34:46.679
Helai,

00:34:47.760 --> 00:34:49.440
need me to help you analyze it?

00:34:49.840 --> 00:34:51.199
Why did you come together today?

00:34:51.579 --> 00:34:53.059
Look at Du Ming,

00:34:54.336 --> 00:34:55.360
bringing cans and fruit.

00:34:55.360 --> 00:34:56.300
How is he?

00:34:56.559 --> 00:34:58.440
Pretty good.
His muscles aren't as stiff.

00:35:04.900 --> 00:35:06.199
What's up, so urgent?

00:35:10.559 --> 00:35:11.059
Du Ming.

00:35:15.579 --> 00:35:17.480
It's nothing big.

00:35:18.079 --> 00:35:19.699
But I need to tell you about it.

00:35:19.900 --> 00:35:21.480
Haven't I been a cop all along?

00:35:21.480 --> 00:35:24.079
I feel like my personality

00:35:25.400 --> 00:35:28.079
always causes trouble,
and you always cover for me.

00:35:28.079 --> 00:35:32.000
And then, well, my family...
My dad farms... You know?

00:35:32.219 --> 00:35:33.480
What is it? Tell me.

00:35:36.059 --> 00:35:36.719
Say it.

00:35:38.760 --> 00:35:40.719
I've quit my job.

00:35:46.079 --> 00:35:46.920
You've quit?

00:35:46.920 --> 00:35:48.820
I'm done. I want to go into business.

00:35:51.760 --> 00:35:52.659
What's going on?

00:35:52.920 --> 00:35:56.420
I want to start a business, earn money,
and improve my family's life.

00:35:56.420 --> 00:35:57.559
That's all.

00:35:57.760 --> 00:35:58.719
Just changing jobs.

00:35:58.719 --> 00:36:01.019
Someone from our township
went into business.

00:36:01.019 --> 00:36:02.639
He made a lot of money and got rich.

00:36:02.639 --> 00:36:04.760
Laosi, you're not joking, are you?

00:36:04.980 --> 00:36:06.960
Just quit being a cop like that?

00:36:08.639 --> 00:36:09.440
I'm done.

00:36:10.139 --> 00:36:11.579
You're a veteran cop too.

00:36:13.500 --> 00:36:14.920
What did you tell me back then?

00:36:16.260 --> 00:36:18.639
Ideals, beliefs, aspirations.

00:36:19.699 --> 00:36:23.139
You swore to me back then. You told me.

00:36:23.639 --> 00:36:25.880
You just quit, all for a bit of money?

00:36:27.860 --> 00:36:30.039
I have to criticize you for this.

00:36:30.760 --> 00:36:31.960
How can you talk like that?

00:36:32.119 --> 00:36:34.272
Laosi's going out

00:36:34.272 --> 00:36:37.312
to build a business and earn some money.

00:36:37.376 --> 00:36:38.960
That's good.

00:36:39.519 --> 00:36:41.960
Everyone can choose
their own path in life, right?

00:36:42.079 --> 00:36:43.659
I'm just changing jobs.

00:36:43.820 --> 00:36:44.320
Yeah.

00:36:44.320 --> 00:36:46.000
I want my dad to live a good life.

00:36:46.400 --> 00:36:48.340
You can't morally judge him
like that, can you?

00:36:51.119 --> 00:36:52.199
I think it's a good thing.

00:36:54.139 --> 00:36:54.880
(Beiyan County Hospital)
Laoda,

00:36:55.639 --> 00:36:58.039
being a cop is draining.

00:37:00.320 --> 00:37:01.360
Cheer up a bit.

00:37:01.880 --> 00:37:05.539
If Laosi wants to try something new,
we should support him, right?

00:37:05.639 --> 00:37:06.559
I understand.

00:37:09.179 --> 00:37:11.979
Helai, what are you doing?

00:37:11.979 --> 00:37:13.219
This is too heavy.

00:37:14.340 --> 00:37:15.860
I don't even know what to say.

00:37:17.639 --> 00:37:19.599
It's not heavy, Du Ming.

00:37:21.119 --> 00:37:21.920
Take care.

00:37:23.659 --> 00:37:24.659
Do well out there.

00:37:26.139 --> 00:37:27.219
Not a cop anymore.

00:37:28.559 --> 00:37:30.639
Earn more money. Don't end up like us.

00:37:32.139 --> 00:37:32.900
Helai,

00:37:34.619 --> 00:37:37.340
I'm just changing jobs. It's the same.

00:37:38.059 --> 00:37:39.320
I'll earn some money.

00:37:40.880 --> 00:37:44.460
The bond between the four of us
will never change.

00:37:47.800 --> 00:37:48.800
I'll head off.

00:37:49.139 --> 00:37:50.000
Take care.

00:37:54.380 --> 00:37:55.880
What are you doing?

00:38:01.460 --> 00:38:02.320
I'm leaving.

00:38:19.380 --> 00:38:20.699
It's your treat from now on.

00:38:45.088 --> 00:38:47.059
(Tile Processing Plant,
Wanchuang Stone Wholesale)

00:38:47.059 --> 00:38:50.639
What? Knowing we've been coming
to the market less lately?

00:38:51.679 --> 00:38:53.500
Thinking about opposing us, huh?

00:38:53.500 --> 00:38:54.840
No, no, no. I wouldn't dare.

00:38:54.960 --> 00:38:56.039
I know I was wrong.

00:38:57.380 --> 00:38:58.139
About what?

00:38:58.460 --> 00:38:59.880
I really wouldn't dare, Hongliang.

00:38:59.880 --> 00:39:01.179
I really know I was wrong.

00:39:01.639 --> 00:39:03.639
I'll pay the management fee.
I'll pay double.

00:39:03.639 --> 00:39:04.760
Whatever you say. I'll pay.

00:39:04.760 --> 00:39:06.340
Whatever you say. I'll pay.

00:39:06.340 --> 00:39:07.139
I'll listen to you.

00:39:07.820 --> 00:39:11.159
It doesn't matter how much you pay now.

00:39:12.679 --> 00:39:18.940
You alone have ruined
the whole market's atmosphere.

00:39:19.199 --> 00:39:20.539
You're quite something.

00:39:20.539 --> 00:39:24.519
Colluding with all the shops,
organizing behind our backs,

00:39:24.519 --> 00:39:27.400
and putting up a fight against us, huh?

00:39:27.400 --> 00:39:28.059
No.

00:39:29.659 --> 00:39:31.900
You really
don't learn your lesson, do you?

00:39:32.480 --> 00:39:34.000
No, Hongkang, Hongliang,

00:39:35.039 --> 00:39:37.039
please give me one last chance.
I'll kowtow to you.

00:39:37.039 --> 00:39:38.079
Hongkang! Hongkang!

00:39:38.380 --> 00:39:39.119
Mr. He.

00:39:39.599 --> 00:39:40.219
Hongkang.

00:39:42.320 --> 00:39:45.099
Mr. He, which hand
do you usually write with?

00:39:50.519 --> 00:39:52.820
This hand? It's a good hand.

00:39:53.400 --> 00:39:56.480
It's just written too many things
it shouldn't have,

00:39:56.480 --> 00:39:57.920
breaking rules.

00:39:59.219 --> 00:40:00.039
Hongkang! Hongliang!

00:40:00.039 --> 00:40:00.820
Come here.

00:40:00.820 --> 00:40:02.079
- Hongkang! Hongliang!
- Come here!

00:40:02.079 --> 00:40:03.079
I know I was wrong!

00:40:03.820 --> 00:40:04.480
Hongkang!

00:40:07.019 --> 00:40:09.159
Hongkang! Hongkang!

00:40:40.288 --> 00:40:48.512
(Tile Processing Plant,
Wanchuang Stone Wholesale)

00:40:50.000 --> 00:40:51.059
They're not human.

00:40:53.719 --> 00:40:54.539
Sis,

00:40:55.320 --> 00:40:57.980
we're all in the same market,
just like family.

00:40:58.460 --> 00:41:00.400
If you have any difficulties ahead,
let me know.

00:41:06.880 --> 00:41:07.559
Mr. He,

00:41:09.179 --> 00:41:10.059
made up your mind?

00:41:17.865 --> 00:41:22.057
(Beiyan County Hospital)

00:41:25.659 --> 00:41:28.860
Zhu, thank you
for making a special trip.

00:41:29.360 --> 00:41:31.380
I was surprised you contacted me.

00:41:32.440 --> 00:41:33.699
You're busy with your business.

00:41:35.500 --> 00:41:37.119
Our relationship

00:41:37.940 --> 00:41:39.139
seems to have drifted apart.

00:41:40.960 --> 00:41:42.219
You're overthinking it, Zhu.

00:41:42.940 --> 00:41:45.840
That market is always hectic.
Busy every single day.

00:41:46.400 --> 00:41:47.659
Let's grab a meal sometime.

00:41:49.900 --> 00:41:50.659
By the way, Zhu,

00:41:51.820 --> 00:41:54.400
given his situation,
will the police arrest those guys?

00:41:55.800 --> 00:41:57.579
Causing permanent disability
to the victim

00:41:58.400 --> 00:42:00.400
constitutes a serious case
of violent assault.

00:42:00.719 --> 00:42:02.579
If verified,
we'll definitely make an arrest.

00:42:04.980 --> 00:42:08.619
So if the case is solid,
how long could they get?

00:42:12.900 --> 00:42:16.380
Guangcai, you persuaded the victim
to report it and contacted me

00:42:17.460 --> 00:42:18.699
exactly for this, right?

00:42:24.059 --> 00:42:25.599
Zhu, I'm not a bad guy.

00:42:27.460 --> 00:42:30.380
Everyone gets bullied in that market.

00:42:32.000 --> 00:42:33.860
I just wanted to be the hero for once.

00:42:57.119 --> 00:42:58.340
(Baima Building Materials Market)
Disperse. Everyone, disperse.

00:43:35.900 --> 00:43:37.880
Qin, look.

00:43:38.119 --> 00:43:39.440
Slow down. Don't fall.

00:43:39.440 --> 00:43:40.288
They arrested them.

00:43:42.800 --> 00:43:44.800
Guangcai. Guangcai, look.

00:43:45.139 --> 00:43:47.659
All taken away. Every last one.

00:43:47.920 --> 00:43:50.000
Keep your voice down. He's studying.

00:43:53.559 --> 00:43:55.860
Here. Have some candy.

00:43:57.579 --> 00:43:58.559
Doesn't your tooth hurt?

00:44:00.139 --> 00:44:02.159
He's studying. Don't disturb him.

00:44:02.159 --> 00:44:03.800
Okay.

00:44:06.559 --> 00:44:08.920
Yes. This one is written well.

00:44:09.659 --> 00:44:11.139
It's better than that one, right?

00:44:11.559 --> 00:44:14.019
What does your mom usually teach you?

00:44:15.019 --> 00:44:16.019
Finish writing it.

00:44:27.940 --> 00:44:29.320
Back at the construction site,

00:44:29.960 --> 00:44:31.119
I never slept well.

00:44:31.880 --> 00:44:33.039
Always on edge.

00:44:34.800 --> 00:44:36.219
Then Xiaoliang got sick,

00:44:37.920 --> 00:44:39.699
and I never slept soundly again.

00:44:45.539 --> 00:44:46.860
Especially when night came,

00:44:49.619 --> 00:44:51.139
I was terrified.

00:44:59.139 --> 00:45:02.659
Is this pronounced 'a' or 'd'?
Or is it 'a'?

00:45:15.559 --> 00:45:16.400
Pretty good.

00:45:23.139 --> 00:45:24.400
About that sign,

00:45:25.900 --> 00:45:28.199
(Baima Building Materials Market)
we'll change it later.

00:45:28.719 --> 00:45:29.460
Change it to what?

00:45:30.260 --> 00:45:31.099
Change it to what?

00:45:31.940 --> 00:45:33.460
Change it to Meng Guangcheng.

00:45:42.340 --> 00:45:43.260
Stop pulling it.

00:45:43.579 --> 00:45:44.300
Wait.

00:45:44.300 --> 00:45:45.119
No.

00:45:46.019 --> 00:45:47.840
Give that to me. Look.

00:45:47.840 --> 00:45:49.139
It's not right, I'm telling you.

00:45:50.400 --> 00:45:51.960
People can see. What are you doing?

00:46:13.199 --> 00:46:16.760
♪Happy birthday to you♪

00:46:17.000 --> 00:46:20.300
♪Happy birthday to you♪

00:46:39.659 --> 00:46:40.500
Huifen!

00:46:41.420 --> 00:46:42.099
Huifen!

00:46:44.840 --> 00:46:47.800
What's this? I went out for groceries,
and you trashed the place.

00:46:48.400 --> 00:46:49.400
Did you touch my stuff?

00:46:50.099 --> 00:46:51.159
Did you touch my sandbox?

00:46:51.519 --> 00:46:52.480
Did you touch this?

00:46:53.400 --> 00:46:55.400
I did a big clean today.
Of course I touched it.

00:46:55.639 --> 00:46:58.360
How many times have I told you?
Don't touch the sandbox.

00:46:58.679 --> 00:46:59.900
One figurine is missing.

00:46:59.900 --> 00:47:02.880
With one piece missing,
I can't reconstruct the crime scene.

00:47:03.079 --> 00:47:04.380
Are you messing with me?

00:47:05.340 --> 00:47:06.320
Me? Messing with you?

00:47:06.860 --> 00:47:09.179
You don't care about me,
a living person right here.

00:47:09.179 --> 00:47:11.440
You care about those stupid figures
on your sandbox.

00:47:11.639 --> 00:47:13.340
Would you notice if I went missing?

00:47:14.119 --> 00:47:15.760
What life am I living, Zhu Helai?

00:47:16.039 --> 00:47:18.139
Look at this room.
Does it look like a bedroom?

00:47:19.179 --> 00:47:22.000
What is all this junk?
Who has this stuff in their bedroom?

00:47:22.480 --> 00:47:24.900
What's hanging up there? Suspect photos?

00:47:25.059 --> 00:47:26.099
Right in my face!

00:47:26.320 --> 00:47:28.639
I get scared going to the bathroom
at night, alright?

00:47:28.639 --> 00:47:31.639
I thought the figurines stood up, so...

00:47:34.000 --> 00:47:34.920
Found it.

00:47:35.659 --> 00:47:36.880
There you are.

00:47:39.920 --> 00:47:41.019
How did you end up here?

00:47:43.159 --> 00:47:44.340
I was so worried.

00:47:44.900 --> 00:47:46.719
It'd be a huge problem
if one were missing.

00:47:46.860 --> 00:47:48.260
Couldn't reconstruct it at all.

00:47:48.980 --> 00:47:51.559
Great. Great. Great.

00:47:53.639 --> 00:47:54.579
Now it's complete.

00:47:55.960 --> 00:47:58.400
This one is here. This one is here.

00:48:00.579 --> 00:48:03.619
You are here. You are here. Yes.

00:48:04.699 --> 00:48:05.659
Perfect.

00:48:07.400 --> 00:48:08.320
Now it's complete.

00:48:18.200 --> 00:48:23.224
=The Silent Rift=